{"id":34531,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/01\/prophets-advice-men-zina\/","url_meta":{"origin":32044,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Chastity: The Prophet\u2019s advice for unmarried young men","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 1, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO young men of Quraysh, do not commit adultery and guard your chastity. No doubt, whoever guards his chastity will certainly enter Paradise.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 6750 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32046,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/guarding-speech-chastity\/","url_meta":{"origin":32044,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Chastity: Guarding speech, controlling lust in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Rafi\u2019 reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever protects what is between his jaws and his thighs, he will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 919 Grade: Jayyid (very good) according to Al-Mundhiri \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0631\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e