ver Allah protects from the evil between his jaws and the evil between his legs, he will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2409 Grade:\u00a0Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9720,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/08\/wife-does-duty-enters-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":32044,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Women: A dutiful wife enters Paradise by any gate","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf a woman prays her five prayers, fasts her month of Ramadan, guards her chastity, and obeys her husband, she will enter Paradise from any gate she wishes.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 4163 Grade:\u00a0Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32463,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/24\/assure-these-six-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32044,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Deeds: Assure these six deeds to enter Para